Related conclusions

About 1% data of each original files was selected for the exploratory analysis. This may not be a large enough sample size.But, a data set that is too large can impede the efficiency of the analysis by placing a burden on the application used for analysis. It is important to find a good balance between sample size and analysis speed/efficiency.

The Goals for Creating the Prediction Algorithm and Shiny

By now, the idea is to use the n-gram to predict next word. But from the app user perspective, the idea is to provide an input field in shiny app that returns the most probable word. The purpose of my completion of this course is to learn the skills that are necessary to develop the products of data analysis and to promote to the people who need them but lack the necessary skills.
